<topic id="oxy-current-selected-element">
  <title><codeph>oxy:current-selected-element()</codeph> Function</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>oxy:current-selected-element function</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>This function returns the fully selected element. If no element is selected, the function
      returns an empty sequence.</p>
    <p><b><u>Example: <i>oxy:current-selected-element</i>
      Function</u></b><codeblock outputclass="language-css">oxy:current-selected-element()[self::p]/b</codeblock></p>
    <p>This example returns the <codeph>b</codeph> elements that are children of the currently
      selected <codeph>p</codeph> element.</p>
  </body>
</topic>
